preference.name: REQ_ExportToExcel_add_level_column
preference.preference_description: Specifies whether Teamcenter inserts the Level column in Microsoft Excel output files for structures that exceed eight levels. In these files, Excel's Outline features are disabled and all objects occupy the same level. The Level column references each object's structure level in Teamcenter. Valid Values: false - The Level column is suppressed. true - The Level column is inserted in the leftmost position.
